cess.nsw.gov.au/Pages/representing/lawassist_readingwritinghome_wysk/lawassist_emailsfaxes_wysk/lawassist_writing_emails.aspx</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b4057b92c38ef802ac28a797fa195d0c2b4f8a","tid":140611,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:53:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補充小小<br />\n律師唔係偵探，唔好諗住得個app名或者域名就查到邊個係持有人。依Ｄ通常IT狗重熟過律師。全香港無得幾多間律師樓有IT Department。</blockquote><br />\n就算要做都唔會搵自己個it department做啦"},{"pid":"b367f7f223ac8f968d167f45268340cb73e7bd52","tid":140611,"uid":26037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:57:23.000Z","msg":"LIHKG 個公開聯絡方式得email的話<br />\n咁出email 律師信有乜問題？"},{"pid":"19925e481ed31bdbdc03d93b5c4337ef99dfc4bf","tid":140611,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LIHKG 個公開聯絡方式得email的話<br />\n咁出email 律師信有乜問題？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0df2bb82eea5c38caf04c7300988c7f86c2e16d","tid":140611,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"其實 attach PDF 有咩問題 。。。<br />\n我公司都收過實體再加 email attach 返個 PDF 。。"},{"pid":"aa2e722af8a86a75a41d35e81c34188e13a31f30","tid":140611,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LIHKG 個公開聯絡方式得email的話<br />\n咁出email 律師信有乜問題？</blockquote><br />\n用email出律師信係無問題，只係班人未見過覺得荒謬<br />\n用email出唔係將內容打係email到，通常係整左封實體信後scan左佢之後作為email既附件咁出"},{"pid":"643369db2adaf4bf77a5da27f4054703332aaf5f","tid":140611,"uid":8632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:09:44.000Z","msg":"班高登打手根本借題發揮<br />\n同五毛一樣都係撩交嗌"},{"pid":"bb18ead0f3b89c8839a7633ed2e26551bcb69979","tid":140611,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":